title: Start
---
$c1: You made it. Good. Then answer quickly-are you here to get me out, or to inspect the site?
-> $c2: I'm here to extract you.
    $c1: Efficient. Good. Then I have a decision to make.
    <<jump VossDecision>>
-> $c2: I'm assessing the situation first.
    $c1: Of course you are. Then I also need to decide how cooperative I'm going to be.
    <<jump VossDecision>>
-> $c2: That depends. Who exactly are you?
    $c1: Aurelia Voss. Executive tier, solar branch, and currently trapped in a building that is trying to become historical rubble.
    $c1: Since identities are now established, I have a decision to make.
    <<jump VossDecision>>
===

title: VossDecision
---
$c1: I can either stay here where it's defensible, or move now while the corridor is still clear enough to risk.

-> $c1: We move now. I refuse to die in a waiting posture.
    $c2: Then stay close and do exactly what I say.
    <<jump EnRoute>>
-> $c1: We hold position. You can clear the route first.
    $c2: Sensible. Then don't wander and don't improvise.
    <<jump HoldPosition>>
-> $c1: Convince me. Why is your plan better than mine?
    $c2: Because hesitation kills faster than bad architecture.
    <<jump C2Followup>>
===

title: C2Followup
---
$c2: So-what is it going to be?
-> $c1: Fine. We move now.
    $c2: Good. On me.
    <<jump EnRoute>>
-> $c1: No. Clear the route first.
    $c2: Then stay put and keep your comms open.
    <<jump HoldPosition>>
===

title: EnRoute
---
$c1: Before we move, one more thing. If we meet someone in the corridor, do you want me quiet, or useful?
-> $c2: Quiet. Let me do the talking.
    $c1: I dislike that answer, which probably means it's tactically sound.
    <<jump ExitPlan>>
-> $c2: Useful. If you see something, say it immediately.
    $c1: Finally, a plan that acknowledges I have a functioning brain.
    <<jump ExitPlan>>
===

title: HoldPosition
---
$c1: Then while you inspect, I need to know what kind of silence this is.
-> $c2: Stay silent unless you're in immediate danger.
    $c1: Understood. Minimal noise, maximal survival.
    <<jump ExitPlan>>
-> $c2: Call out the moment you notice anything change.
    $c1: Excellent. Anxiety with a reporting structure.
    <<jump ExitPlan>>
===

title: ExitPlan
---
$c1: All right. We understand each other.
$c2: Then let's act like it.
===